reviewText: Love this group of videos. Uplifting and inspiring
I received this cd yesterday, and it doesn't even play. I have tried 5 other cd players, and it states that it is not playable.
2012 was a great year for the Gospel industry, lots of hits and lots of different styles and performances.  I loved this DVD!

Great videos although Vashaun other song was there which I also love. My children can't stop playing the videos. (quick shipping to t&T too)
Looking forward for a wow Christmas dvd someday
Where are the rest of the videos...simply incomplete! I would not have purchase if I had knew this did not have ALL the videos on the DVD.

I actually sent it back as ordered the wrong thing... I thought it was a music cd. but would not play in my cd player, as it was a audio cd. but the cd played just fine in dvd player. just wasn't really what I wanted.
Out of all the WOW Gospel's I have, this is by far the very best one. It arrived ahead of time so I got to enjoy it right away. 2 thumbs up.
